The wait is over, Alternative is finally upon us!!!

To the newcomers:

This is the third part of an epic trilogy with a slow start and it holds the #1 position on VNDB’s rating list.

I highly recommend following this order for maximum enjoyment:

1) 14 episode anime “Kimi ga Nozomu Eien” (set in the same universe as “Muv-Luv Extra”, it introduces some important characters);

2) 3 episode “Akane Maniax” anime (follows the story of “Kimi ga Nozomu Eien“ and introduces the cast of “Muv-Luv Extra”);

3) Muv-Luv Extra (first game);

4) Muv-Luv Unlimited (second game);

5) Muv-Luv Alternative.

* The first two games (“Extra” and “Unlimited”) are sold together under the title “Muv-Luv”.
* There is a patch if you want the +18 content for Extra and Unlimited.
* The Kimi ga Nozomu Eien anime is an adaptation of a visual novel that is planned to be translated in the future.

